From: Luwei Zhou <b45643@freescale.com>
Date: Wed, 2 Apr 2014 13:36:22 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0374/1074] ENGR00306569: ARM: dts: imx6sx-sdb: Add mma8451
 sensor dts support

This patch add mma8451 sensor device tree support on i.MX6SX-SDB
platform.

Signed-off-by: Luwei Zhou <b45643@freescale.com>
[Original patch taken from git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git]
Signed-off-by: Biyao Zhai <biyao.zhai@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts |    6 ++++++
 1 files changed, 6 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts
index d278658..44bfb26 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts
@@ -336,6 +336,12 @@
 		interrupts = <5 1>;
 		shared-interrupt;
 	};
+
+	mma8451@1c {
+		compatible = "fsl,mma8451";
+		reg = <0x1c>;
+		position = <1>;
+	};
 };
 
 &i2c4 {
